AN ACT
HB628 INTRODUCED
29
30 Relating to elections; to amend Sections 17-4-3 and
31 17-4-9, Code of Alabama 1975, and Sections 17-4-30 and
32 17-4-39, Code of Alabama 1975, as amended by Act 2025-424 of
33 the 2025 Regular Session; to establish a 90-day period before
34 any regular election held in the state where no board of
35 registrars may purge, make inactive, or otherwise remove an
36 elector from the statewide voter registration list; and to
37 make nonsubstantive, technical revisions to update the
38 existing code language to current style.
39 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
40 Section 1. Sections 17-4-3 and 17-4-9, Code of Alabama
41 1975, and Sections 17-4-30 and 17-4-39, Code of Alabama 1975
42 as amended by Act 2025-424 of the 2025 Regular Session, are
43 amended to read as follows:
