52 moral turpitude for the purposes of Article VIIISection 177 of
53 the Constitution of Alabama of 19012022 since being
54 registered, or otherwise become disqualified as an elector.
55 Except as provided below, a person in subdivisions (2) and
56 (3), an individual convicted of a disqualifying criminal
